headline.main: No. 20 Saint Mary's Beats Portland 81-58 in WCC Quarterfinal
headline.print_headline: No. 20 Saint Mary's Beats Portland 81-58 in WCC Quarterfinal

lead_paragraph: China's top economic official trimmed the country's growth target and warned Sunday of dangers from global pressure for trade controls as Beijing tries to build a consumer-driven economy and reduce reliance on exports and investment.
